{"tid":974529,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：難民對美國構成人道危機　重申要求撥款建圍牆","createTime":"2019-01-09T03:16:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T06:58:27.000Z","uid":141151,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6e38051e9e570f134c09fe0de147aeb05ff21a52","tid":974529,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T03:16:18.000Z","msg":"特朗普：難民對美國構成人道危機　重申要求撥款建圍牆<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1437161-20190109.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1437161-20190109.htm&d=WIb3OhKSmvf3RGtiUmTrWJzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=09763284\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1437161-20190109.htm&h=e0d4246b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1437161-20190109.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普發表全國電視講話，他表示，美國正面臨人道危機，必須立即行動。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">特朗普在白宮橢圓型辦公室發表演說，認為美墨邊境的危機日益惡化，強調圍牆對國家安全至為關鍵，可作為屏障防止難民湧入，打破拉丁美洲難民湧入的惡性循環，而受到傷害的大多數是婦女同兒童，形容這只是「普通常識」。</span><br />\n<br />\n特朗普要求國會撥款57億美元作為邊境安全開支，又說應民主黨人要求，同意興建鋼鐵屏障，而非混凝土牆。<br />\n<br />\n但特朗普在演說中未有宣布國家進入緊急狀態。<br />\n<br />\n由於白宮與國會因為未能解決興建邊境圍牆撥款的爭議，聯邦政府自上月22日起局部停止運作。"},{"pid":"55f8cc4c6573b02b85f5c9541ab2634e821fc958","tid":974529,"uid":146257,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T03:26:32.000Z","msg":"57億美金都要咁大陣仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地香港570億美金都唔洗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa9e3a2d4941ad5a928eed09cbbd7a357f9c6fd","tid":974529,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55f8cc4c6573b02b85f5c9541ab2634e821fc958","tid":974529,"uid":146257,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T03:26:32.000Z","msg":"57億美金都要咁大陣仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地香港570億美金都唔洗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/g